About the game:

Take a vibrant journey to the land of Fuzz and meet some quirky little characters. Can you rescue the cuddly Iggles from the evil Zoogs? Move your Iggle friends to their color-coded destinations and pop them out of their bubble prisons. Be sure to listen to Doc Iggle ... he's got all the tips and tricks you'll need to set these loveable Iggles free!
